The Minister of Education, Adamu Adamu and the chairman of the All Progressive Congress, (APC), Mai Mala Buni paid a courtesy visit to president Muhammadu Buhari in London. Mai Mala Buni and Minister Adamu Adamu visited the president in London to check on his health. The outfit of president Muhammadu Buhari got people talking on social media.
Some of the pictures of president Muhammadu Buhari, Mai Mala Buni and the Nigerian Minister of of Education, Adamu Adamu on social media.
Take a look at the pictures of president Muhammadu Buhari that caused a lot of stir on social media below.

The pictures really got people talking because of the unusual dressing of president Muhammadu Buhari, Some people said he really look smart and young in the outfit that he wore.
